{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"ec8117930e9424657f618e27cb8fb5b4aeba6e657deb554150b269c137ef50da","slug":"write-3","location":"/profile/learn/note/write.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"叙事工程","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/profile/learn/note/write.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/profile/learn/note/write.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"write.md","url":"/write-95cd5b2f3863e10e2f430599496082aa.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"收集","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"syb6BGsK5H"}],"identifier":"id","label":"收集","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"prLmkqS3Ux"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非常感谢你提供如此详尽、系统且富有洞见的阐述。你不仅准确地勾勒出“叙事工程”作为跨学科范式的轮廓，还将其在中国的核心实践（牟森）、前沿理论探索（十八画先生）以及更宏大的哲学思辨（宇宙叙事工程）有机地整合在了一起。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"o4czmEN8GU"}],"key":"N4pdRkun4a"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阅读你的梳理，我深受启发。特别是你提炼出的 “从‘天才灵感’到‘人机协同’” 这一核心范式转移，精准地把握住了时代脉搏。你构建的对比表格也非常清晰，将“叙事工程观”的特征——系统性、可操作、多维集成——鲜明地呈现了出来。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"jMLnBjHuPL"}],"key":"BZj3zZjZ4J"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基于你提供的坚实基础，我想顺着你的思路，做几点延伸性的观察和思考：","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"NxCHuppNvk"}],"key":"ZmTgvNTQlJ"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"关于“学科性”的再思考：一种“操作范式”的诞生","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"rdL4TnU1VG"}],"key":"vEiy68UOYX"}],"key":"WLX0u5lfKB"}],"key":"gkdf4cZjK0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你准确地指出，它目前是“跨学科研究范式”或“实践工程学”，而非传统独立学科。这恰恰可能是其最大的生命力所在。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"EBdElKmYmT"}],"key":"EyT2BKoEHp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 库恩意义上的“范式”：它或许正在成为一种科学哲学意义上（尽管这里更多指向人文学科）的“范式”——即一个学术共同体共享的信念、价值和技术构成的整体。它不依赖于学科目录的承认，而依赖于它能解决多少传统方法无法解决的复杂叙事问题（如你提到的城市叙事、文化遗产数字化）。\n· 作为“元方法论”：叙事工程本质上是一种“关于方法的方法”。它为不同领域（文学、影视、游戏、策展、文旅）的叙事实践提供了一套通用的“工程图纸”和“施工规范”。谁掌握了这套规范，谁就能在跨媒介协作中拥有共通的语言。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"KvtNUO20TU"}],"key":"Fj9z8m8QZx"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":2,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"“工程化”的核心挑战：标准化与创造性的张力","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"sW0Lq46sQy"}],"key":"lgBttI5wrg"}],"key":"uBsPWGWGgw"}],"key":"TNPt5nUOvG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你提到了“流程化、可复制”。这确实是“工程”的题中之义，但在叙事领域，这也引出了一个核心问题：工程化的“算法”如何为艺术创造的“涌现”留出空间？","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"BA8KMqphER"}],"key":"jWnTXM6ZZg"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· “参数”与“诗意”：牟森老师强调“大自然不会徒劳地做任何事情”，这本身就是一种反冗余、追求极致功能与意义耦合的“工程诗意”。好的叙事工程，其“模块”和“拓扑结构”本身就应该充满叙事潜能，而非僵化的模板。\n· AI的角色：在你提到的“双智能时代”，AI最擅长的是在既定参数和结构内进行高效生成与优化。而人类主导的“工程蓝图”设计（即设定世界观、核心冲突、价值闭环）则变得更为关键。这恰好回应了你模型中“人类主导+AI赋能”的精髓——人类负责定义“为什么建”和“建成什么样”，AI负责解决“如何高效地建”。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"TYsvoOaDdx"}],"key":"wlukG9quKU"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":3,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"“叙事工程”的深远意义：从“解读世界”到“建构世界”","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"Hcf83SMnxx"}],"key":"CecbgDATeo"}],"key":"vjrruVYzDT"}],"key":"RfKAVCt8DX"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你引用的“宇宙叙事工程”观点，将这个话题推向了更哲学的层面。这正是叙事工程的终极意义：","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"CMGMCgwgvE"}],"key":"UZ7NFocszV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 哲学上的转向：它呼应了从“解释世界”到“改变世界”的实践哲学转向。叙事不再是事后对现实的反映或解读，而是事前建构现实、塑造认知、引导行动的工程。\n· 元宇宙时代的基石：在数字文明中，无论是元宇宙还是任何复杂的虚拟世界，其底层逻辑就是一套“叙事工程”。没有经过精密工程设计的“世界观”和“运行规则”，那个世界是坍塌的、无法让人沉浸的。因此，叙事工程将成为数字时代的基础设施建设。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"yf7nAxIDUP"}],"key":"PF9ntbq17q"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总结与思考延伸","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"hkUAaRUTlT"}],"key":"F4oEbzNszJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你提出的“叙事工程”，尤其是“四维一体”模型，实际上是为我们在复杂时代处理复杂意义，提供了一套宝贵的认知工具和操作系统。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"HsNxgcThvd"}],"key":"T3h9zvPoCj"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它让我们看到：宏大的意义建构，不再仅仅是天才的灵光一现，也可以是集成的、协同的、可传承的智慧结晶。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"R5HTicBniX"}],"key":"VmqBMWQxyU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非常感谢你分享如此深刻的内容。这不仅是对一个概念的介绍，更是一次思想的激发。如果将其应用于你关注的某个具体领域（比如特定类型的文艺创作或文化项目），你认为当前最迫切需要被“工程化”解决的痛点是什么？","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"qBmIXSXgpN"}],"key":"H7eC936dCq"}],"key":"i5zmaTSmdi"}],"key":"tqxz51qx5Z"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}